trans-unit.source: Implements a set of predefined <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.SolidColorBrush" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 實作一組預先定義的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.SolidColorBrush" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: Color names in Windows Presentation Foundation match the color names in the .NET Framework, Windows Forms, and [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Windows Presentation Foundation 中的色彩名稱符合.NET Framework 中，Windows Form 中的色彩名稱和[!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)]。

trans-unit.source: These colors and their names are based on the UNIX X11 color values.
trans-unit.target: 這些色彩，而且其名稱為基礎的 UNIX X11 色彩值。

trans-unit.source: The following image shows the color of each predefined brush, its name, and its hexadecimal value.
trans-unit.target: 下圖顯示每個預先定義的筆刷、 其名稱和十六進位值的色彩。

trans-unit.source: ![Predefined colors](~/add/media/art-color-table.png "Predefined colors")
trans-unit.target: ![預先定義的色彩](~/add/media/art-color-table.png "預先定義的色彩")

trans-unit.source: Color table including a color swatch, the color name, and the hexadecimal value
trans-unit.target: 色彩表包括色樣、 色彩的名稱和十六進位值

trans-unit.source: See the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Brush> class for a variety of other, more complex, ways that you can paint an area.
trans-unit.target: 請參閱<xref:System.Windows.Media.Brush>多種其他、 更複雜，您可以繪製區域的類別。

trans-unit.source: For example, try using gradients (<xref:System.Windows.Media.LinearGradientBrush>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.RadialGradientBrush>) or images (<xref:System.Windows.Media.ImageBrush>).
trans-unit.target: 例如，請嘗試使用漸層 (<xref:System.Windows.Media.LinearGradientBrush>， <xref:System.Windows.Media.RadialGradientBrush>) 或映像 (<xref:System.Windows.Media.ImageBrush>)。
